Master design doc

HLD:

Fantasy
Top-down (2d, overhead)
no inventory

3 slots
melee weapon
ranged weapon
magic slot
shield/optional slot?

A-La zelda style, top level world with seperate sub dugeons

Major Questions:
	Overall Art design
	Story

Level Design:
	32 x 24 tiles
		4 L,R reserved for HUD = 28 x 24

	File Format -> tile prop

	World:
		World -> 20 x 20 (N,S,E,W)

		{
		size x
		size y
		
		<name> <n exit> <s exit> <ER...> //eg <G11> <_> <G12> <ER....>
		}
	Map:
		{
		name
		<size> // 28,24
		[RSC]
		. -> No

		{any ascii} #, ..../fname

		[AT]
		.
		.
		.
		D,D,D,D,D
		[UNDER]
		.
		.
		.
		[ENTITY]
		.
		.
		.
		.
		}

